{"tid":573900,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"坐地鐵想好好補眠可以點(有圖解教學)","createTime":"2018-02-27T01:59:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-27T03:59:26.000Z","uid":44665,"like":3,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"68a7be95cba2ab8a37f58d994a00cb6bb950b179","tid":573900,"uid":44665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T01:59:02.000Z","msg":"學生哥功課，打工OT到好夜，第二朝都會好夜訓。坐長途車如果可以搵到個靚位訓教就好了。坐地鐵，識簡一定爺第二個位！<br />\n<br />\n1. 最尾果個位使用率極高，通常一開閘正常人都會狗衝果個位，好多人都會靠住玻璃訓教。長年累月玻璃上面會積左好多頭油同面油<br />\n<br />\n2. 第二個位有窗框，可以卡住個頭唔會跌，靠住訓成程都oj。傳說中國製冇咁好卡，窗框比較淺。建議上車前，睇清楚係咪中國製先好上車。<br />\n<br />\n祝大家有個愉快旅程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n(圖解)<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/27/095637_fc7e959cd577e5a6aed8719093524005.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F27%2F095637_fc7e959cd577e5a6aed8719093524005.png&h=c99b6397&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nIG ：<a href=\"http://www.instagram.com/arjostory/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Farjostory%2F&d=u9aNrW9w0vJ2xZCPsOckSUkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=37ebab7f\" target=\"_blank\">www.instagram.com/arjostory/</a><br />\nFacebook : <a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/arjostory/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Farjostory%2F&d=u9aNrW9w0vJ2xZCPsOckSUkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=441cd1f6\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/arjostory/</a>"},{"pid":"d2accae3ad251f2a18247e5106a2cf3f93eb4534","tid":573900,"uid":21423,"like":32,"dislike":11,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T02:15:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"045306433229d99370efabb861810caf65704373","tid":573900,"uid":20449,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T02:16:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"47d2e14c8a8c2050589f33225ef5367eae4bf336","tid":573900,"uid":21423,"like":12,"dislike":8,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018